  "description": {
    "zh": "没错，我就是Mechanic。我现在事情的多的很，有话就直说了，你想来帮忙是吗？PLC100用的编程元件坏掉了，时间又很紧，真是尴尬。订单还要发货。随便吧，我为什么要和你说这些呢。我需要你给我配一支MP-133霰弹枪，我没时间去做这件事，手上还缺点零件。这把枪的人机功效应当高于47，要有激光指示器、加长弹仓和小于850的总后座力。还要足够紧凑，不能超过4格。你找到了咱们再谈别的。",
    "en": "Hello, mercenary. I don't have much time today, plus the programmer unit for PLC100 is out of order, so let's get straight to business. I build various weapons with modifications for my clients, and I'll need some help with it.\n\nI need you to mod an MP-133 shotgun. I won’t have time to build it myself, and I don't have parts for it either anyway. This gun should have more than 47 ergonomics, a laser designator, an extended mag, and less than 850 recoil sum. And make it compact, too, not more than 4 slots. Build one for me, and I'll pay you well."
  },
